Objectives:
At the end of phase 2, all students should be able to :
● Create basic BDD framework
● Create, edit and complete basic Jira components like test, test set, test execution, bug,
etc.
● Automating smoke tests
● Start building regression suite
Sprint 3:
During the first sprint, teams will:
● Develop BDD test automation framework
● Automate test cases created during the first phase
● Create Jira tests for every test case in the BDD framework
● Start automating smoke tests
● Start creating regression suite